album.description:
Plantarium.INFO. Plant anatomy, Hybrids, Pests and Diseases, Carnivorous, Myco-Heterotrophic, Parasitic, Albinos, Fungi, Succulents, Cactuses, Aquatic, Nut-fruited, Tuberous, Ferns, Mosses, Bulbs, Mutants, Witches' brooms, Fairy rings, Prolific petals, Bad luck, Good luck, Colors, Burls, Mycelium, Molds, Journeys.

Visit also Main site of plants and herbs: Herbarium.INFO
